ZH: 我们很抱歉，这张机票已经被取消，您需要退票。
EN: We apologize, but this flight ticket has been canceled, you need to request a refund.
ZH: 请问您想要全额退票还是只退一部分？
EN: Would you like a full refund or only a partial refund?
ZH: 由于航班延误，您可以选择免费退票或改签。
EN: Due to flight delays, you can choose to request a free refund or reschedule.
ZH: 请您在申请退票前仔细查看退票政策。
EN: Please carefully review the refund policy before requesting a refund.
ZH: 您可以在网上或者到机场柜台办理退票手续。
EN: You can process the refund procedure online or at the airport counter.
ZH: 对不起，这张火车票已经过了改签与退票的期限。
EN: I'm sorry, but this train ticket is past the deadline for changing or refunding.
ZH: 买了一张错票，现在只能退票了。
EN: I bought the wrong ticket, now I can only request a refund.
ZH: 请在出发前48小时内提出退票申请。
EN: Please submit the refund request at least 48 hours before departure.
ZH: 请填写完整的乘客信息以便办理退票手续。
EN: Please provide complete passenger information for the refund process.
ZH: 退票需要扣除一定的手续费用。
EN: There will be a certain amount of handling fee deducted for the refund.
ZH: 我们会在收到退票申请后的7个工作日内处理。
EN: We will process the refund request within 7 working days after receiving it.
ZH: 对不起，该航班已不接受任何形式的改签或退票。
EN: I'm sorry, but this flight no longer accepts any form of rebooking or refund.
ZH: 他们因为个人原因需要退票。
EN: They need to request a refund due to personal reasons.
ZH: 由于铁路工程原因，列车取消了，所有乘客可以选择退票或改签。
EN: Due to railway construction reasons, the train has been canceled, all passengers can choose to request a refund or reschedule.
ZH: 非特殊情况下购买的机票一经售出即不可退票。
EN: Flight tickets purchased under normal circumstances are non-refundable once sold.
ZH: 请持有效身份证件前来办理退票手续。
EN: Please bring valid identification to process the refund procedure.
ZH: 由于天气原因，邮轮行程取消，请乘客前往退票窗口进行处理。
EN: Due to weather reasons, the cruise itinerary has been canceled, please go to the refund window for processing.
ZH: 经过处理，您的退票申请已成功，并将于3个工作日内返还退款。
EN: Your refund request has been successfully processed and the refund will be returned within 3 working days.
